\ProvidesClass{edgemind-ptc}[2014/01/19, Edgemind technical and commercial proposal, V1.0]

% Class edgemind-tpc
%
% Latex class to write a technical and commercial proposal with the EdgeMind graphical identity.
%
% TODO :
